text: Chandar () is a rural locality (a village) in Krasnoklyuchevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 220 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Krasnaya Gorka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Chandar, Republic of Bashkortostan
